How does SHE do it? Sarah Jessica Parker and Olivia Munn overshadowed by buxom Christina Hendricks at their premiere



It is a film starring one of Hollywood's most stylish women, premièring in the middle of Fashion Week. So the New York screening of I Don't Know How She Does It was, unsurprisingly, a fashionable event tonight.



But the film's star Sarah Jessica Parker while stylish as ever, was overshadowed by her co-star Christina Hendricks' jaw-dropping look on the red carpet.
